HEADWORD: Horribleness
<hw>Hor"ri*ble*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state or quality of
being horrible; dreadfulness; hideousness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>horribleness</qex> of the mischief.</q> <rj><qau>Sir P.
Sidney.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Horribly</ent>⟦br⟧
